Drops & Wins

Pragmatic Play presents: an entire year of weekly tournaments and daily prize drops, with a combined prize pool of 1,000,000 EUR a month! The money prizes don’t have a wagering requirement — win them and take them!

The promo runs from February 9, 2022 to February 8, 2023. To participate in the promo, make qualifying bets of 0.50+ EUR in the participating games and win. Once you win, you can watch your progress on the leaderboards.

Each tournament runs for seven days from Wednesday (18:01 UTC) to Wednesday (17:59 UTC), with daily Prize Drops running at the same time.

Each of your qualifying spins may trigger a random Prize Drop prize. Watch the tables in the participating games — they update in real time. You may win multiple Prize Drop prizes every day!

There are two types of tournaments: slots and Live Casino.

To win the slots tournaments, play the participating slots and try to score as high as possible on the leaderboard. The criteria is to earn the highest single spin win amount (adjusted to the bet value). The higher the score, the better the prize!

The Drops & Wins slots include:

  1. Cash prizes — 6,500,000 EUR in total
  2. From February 9, 2022 to February 8, 2023 — 500,000 EUR monthly
  3. 52 weekly tournaments with a prize pool of 62,000 EUR
  4. 364 daily Prize Drops with a daily prize pool of 9,000 EUR

The Drops & Wins Live Casino includes:

The Drops & Wins Live Casino includes three different prize drops:

  1. Prize Drops (minimum bet is 1 EUR);
  2. Mega Drops (minimum bet is 5 EUR);
  3. Daily Blackjack Prize Drops (minimum 25 EUR).

Prize Drops run every Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, and Sunday. Mega Drops run every Friday and Saturday. Daily Blackjack Prize Drops run daily.

All those Live Casino drops are limited to a certain list of tables that are listed in the full version of Drops & Wins rules.
